is known from the 
<collectingCountry box="[487,591,248,275]" name="Seychelles" pageId="53" pageNumber="60">Seychelles</collectingCountry>
only, where it is restricted to Silhouette (
<geoCoordinate box="[468,540,279,306]" degrees="4" direction="south" minutes="30" orientation="latitude" pageId="53" pageNumber="60" precision="925" value="-4.5">4°30’S</geoCoordinate>
, 
<geoCoordinate box="[550,636,279,306]" degrees="55" direction="east" minutes="15" orientation="longitude" pageId="53" pageNumber="60" precision="925" value="55.25">55°15’E</geoCoordinate>
) and Mahé (
<geoCoordinate box="[230,302,311,338]" degrees="4" direction="south" minutes="45" orientation="latitude" pageId="53" pageNumber="60" precision="925" value="-4.75">4°45’S</geoCoordinate>
, 
<geoCoordinate box="[311,398,311,338]" degrees="55" direction="east" minutes="30" orientation="longitude" pageId="53" pageNumber="60" precision="925" value="55.5">55°30’E</geoCoordinate>
